item.description:
Reminder Memo of Early October Meet Up.

I want to have a chance to meet with our members in early October to
Discuss our busy October calendar of events.

We have many new members and members who have not come
To a Meet Up in a long time.

We can discuss what kind of Meet Ups that we can look forward to
After October. I can use feedback from our members to
Schedule future Meet Ups.

Duchess Diner is on Campbell Avenue right next to the
Rail Road tracks with parking next to the rail road tracks and
Just behind the restaurant. I will probably be parked behind the
Restaurant.

You do not have order a meal.
You can just order a coffee or any other drink and just
Chat with the group.
